data.description: A warm, inviting, highly upgraded and spotless Savannah model home in Saguaro Bloom, a fabulous newer community in Northwest Tucson, is now welcoming potential buyers. It's bright and open, with views of Sombrero Peak from most windows and the lovely rear yard. Large windows and glass doors bring the outside in, allowing a sense of connection with nature. Guests enter your new home through an enclosed entry with a handsome low gate, and this design is echoed in the screen door which allows a cross breeze on spring days. A foyer with a dramatic 20' ceiling lit by glass panels leads to the open kitchen, family room and breakfast space, with a vast island as a focal point once one has noticed the stunning views of Sombrero Peak. Quartz counters provide ample workspace for multiple chefs, along with a large stainless steel sink, and a walk-in pantry. Upgraded cabinets and tile backsplash add to the beauty of this home. A large dining area adjacent to the family room overlooks the garden and provides more views. Step out to a covered patio with electric sunscreen and a large yard featuring an excellent outdoor kitchen with both gas and charcoal grills, a cooking burner, and a refrigerator, fabulous for entertaining. Fabulous mature landscaping adds to the attractiveness of the garden. Back inside, there is an office space with glass doors. The Owners' Suite, accessed by double doors, is gloriously large with space for a sofa and dressers to augment the walk-in closet. The spacious Owners' bath area is well-lit and has separate counters. The handsome counters are "Piedra Fina" upgraded cultured stone. The laundry room has been upgraded to include storage cabinets, a stainless sink and a space for hanging clothes to dry. Two guest bedrooms share a bath, while a third small bedroom is used as a library & den. The Saguaro Bloom community includes many amenities: Multiple neighborhood parks, a community center available for meetings and parties, an exercise facility, Community Pool and nearby excellent schools. It has been a friendly and comfortable neighborhood for these homeowners and has a reputation for welcoming incoming homeowners. Please call for your private showing of this move-in-ready home.
